official_title: A Hybrid Effectiveness-Implementation Study on Weight Gain Prevention Among 2-1-1 Callers
inclusion_criteria:
* 18 to 70 years of age
* able to speak English
* self-report BMI of 20 and above
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must have minimum age of 18 Years
Must have maximum age of 70 Years
exclusion_criteria:
* pregnant women
* only one member per household will be enrolled
